skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: food tracker
des:
Disclaim: This skill is Not sponsored or endorsed by SeattleFoodTruck.com and Food Truck Finder.
This skill will help you explore the the food truck in Seattle, and find the location of your selected food truck. Information accuracy can be varied time to time.
This will only help you find the location of the food trucks which provided their time and location on-line.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
